### Event Management Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@orgToken = YOUR_ORG_ACCESS_TOKEN
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1. [PUBLIC] Get Event Metadata (Categories & Cities)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/meta

### 2. [PUBLIC] List Approved Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events
# Optional: ?categoryId=1&cityId=1&search=Jazz

### 3. [ORGANIZER] Create New Event
# NOTE: Ensure your organizer profile is APPROVED first!
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgToken}}

{
    "title": "Abyssinia Jazz Night",
    "description": "An exclusive evening of Ethio-Jazz.",
    "venue": "Sheraton Addis",
    "dateTime": "2025-12-30T19:00:00Z",
    "eventType": "CAPACITY",
    "totalCapacity": 500,
    "categoryId": 2,
    "cityId": 1,
    "tiers": [
        { "name": "Regular", "price": 1000, "capacity": 400 },
        { "name": "VIP", "price": 3000, "capacity": 100 }
    ]
}

### 4. [ADMIN] List All Events for Review
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/admin/list
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. [ADMIN] Review & Approve Event
# Replace :id with the Event ID from Request #4
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/1/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "status": "APPROVED",
    "commission": 15.0
}
